The paper focuses on the security of IoT devices, which is a major concern in the field of computer security (cs.CR). The proposed approach involves the strategic deployment of defense mechanisms, which is related to network security (cs.NI) and software engineering (cs.SE). The use of a multi-objective genetic algorithm also suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and systems and control (cs.SY).
